aster','Full-time','Male','D:\\resumes\\Michael_Brown_Resume.pdf','2025-08-20 19:40:28'),(14,'Sophia Martinez','sophia_m','sophia.martinez.es@gmail.com','SophM@rt99','+34 612 345 678','Fresher','Diploma','Part-time','Female','D:\\resumes\\Sophia_Martinez_Resume.pdf','2025-08-20 19:42:40'),(15,'Rajesh Kumar','rajeshk','rajesh.kumar.iitb@gmail.com','RajKum#55','+91 91234 56789','Senior','Bachelor','Full-time','Male','D:\\resumes\\Rajesh_Kumar_Resume.pdf','2025-08-20 19:43:35'),(16,'Hannah Lee','hannah_lee','Master’s Degree','HanLee@77','86 138 0013 7486','Fresher','Master','Full-time','Female','D:\\resumes\\Hannah_Lee_Resume.pdf','2025-08-20 19:44:58'),(17,'Omar Farouk','omar_farouk','omar.farouk.eg@yahoo.com','OmarF#2025','+20 100 234 5678','Fresher','High School','Part-time','Male','D:\\resumes\\Omar_Farouk_Resume.pdf','2025-08-20 19:45:56'),(18,'Zoe Anderson','zoe_anderson','zoe.anderson.au@gmail.com','ZAnder$88','+61 412 345 678','Senior','Bachelor','Full-time','Female','D:\\resumes\\Zoe_Anderson_Resume.pdf','2025-08-20 19:47:15'),(19,'test','test','testgmail.com','123','1234344546','Fresher','High School','Full-time','Male','C:\\Users\\hnine\\Downloads\\Chapter 6-3.pdf','2025-08-23 02:01:17'),(22,'test343','test234','test@gmail','123','1231231414','Fresher','High School','Full-time','Male',NULL,'2025-08-23 02:15:45'),(23,'test12','tests2124','tdtzsa@gmail.com','123','2414322355','Junior','High School','Full-time','Male','C:\\Users\\hnine\\Downloads\\Chapter 2-6.pdf','2025-08-23 02:22:49'),(25,'seeker','seeker123','seeker@gmail.com','123','09123445647234354545','Fresher','High School','Full-time','Male',NULL,'2025-08-23 03:45:48'),(27,'seeker','seeker99','seeker99@gmail.com','123','24344546567','Fresher','High School','Full-time','Male',NULL,'2025-08-23 03:55:26'),(28,'Tenshi Lin','tenshi_x02','tenshi.enforcerx02@example.com','EnfX02!7qvA','0977654321','Junior','Bachelor','Full-time','Female','uploads/resumes/seeker28/Tenshi_Lin_Resume.pdf','2025-08-23 07:06:22');
